SCP-3719: Your Friendly Neighbourhood Lawnmower


20 Mar 2018 03:27








SCP-3719:  Your Friendly Neighbourhood Lawnmower

Author:  Lt Flops
附加记录：    
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Hi all, here’s my third SCP. This idea has been sitting in my head for about a year now, but I hadn't figured out how to write it until recently. My initial idea was to write a lawnmower that slowly degrades the bonds between neighbours. Tanhony gave me the alternate idea that it should form the bond between neighbours by attaching them together physically. Thanks to him for that!
